    "description": "Grow your career with Bandhan Bank Advisory Limited! We are hiring a Risk Analyst for our Delhi team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Bandhan Bank Advisory Limited:\nBandhan Bank Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in Power BI\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Budgeting\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Referral bonus program\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Learning & development budget\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Bandhan Bank Advisory Limited!",
